title: Chanel Medallion Tote Bag
description: Chanel Medallion tote bag in black diamond-quilted caviar leather (#74xxxxx: 2002-2003). Featuring gold-tone hardware, exterior rear patch pocket, stitched CC logo at front, and rolled leather handles. The zipper closure with CC logo accent opens to a black leather interior with zip & patch pockets. Approx dimensions: 29.5cm(Base-L) x 23.5cm(H) x 14.5cm(D), 16cm shoulder drop. Accompanied by a Chanel dustbag and authentication card. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
